<body>
<h1>GeoShowcase</h1>
<div>
<p>Example: search for ski runs within a radius of 10 km from the city of Trento: Lat. 46.071, Lon. 11.120</p>
<form action="geometry" method="get">
 Lat.<input type="text" name="latitude" size="10" /><br/>
 Lon.<input type="text" name="longitude" size="10" /><br/>
 Radius (km)<input type=text" name="radius" size="10" /><br/>
 <input type="submit" value="Send"/>
</form>
</div>
</body>
